title: Fix typo in ProjectCacheService.IsDesignTimeBuild leading to the value of BuildingProject not being checked
body:
Fix typo in ProjectCacheService.IsDesignTimeBuild leading to the value of BuildingProject not being checked.

This is a regression in #7833, probably due to bad copy/paste while refactoring.

Thanks @davkean for spotting this bug!

commit.message: Fix typo in ProjectCacheService.IsDesignTimeBuild leading to the value of BuildingProject not being checked
